\"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty)  \\\"Raygun\\\", Australia's Olympic breakdancer has returned with new dance moves after being the subject of non-stop online memes.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.941202109986171, \"rank\": 0.05516973233459248, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The country's first Olympic breakdancer Rachael Gunnwent viral onlineafter debuting her unconventional moves at the inaugural Olympic breaking competition on 9 August.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999996623501, \"rank\": 1.9680356709233999e-10, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event saw two live DJs, with competitors undergoing three judged battles, involving two 60-second routines each, before eliminations and medals were awarded.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes were judgedon creativity, personality, technique, variety, musicality and vocabulary, which means the variation and quantity of moves.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, Gunn did not earn any points in any of her three battles.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since her performance, Gunn has been subjected to a slew of online criticism after failing to receive any points from the judges at the Olympics and was knocked out at the round-robin stage of the competition.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the star returned to give fans one last show in Paris.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999882222262, \"rank\": 1.1777783572136293e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage captured by Olympic Australian diver Domonic Bedggood showed the 36-year-old breaker taking to the streets with some new moves alongside fellow athletes.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999844491853288, \"rank\": 1.3497513094927096e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\", \"score\": 0.9999999396868606, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Domonic Bedggood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appearing to dance to Bruno Mars and Mark Ronson's \\\"Uptown Funk\\\", Gunn - who was named the top-ranked B-girl by the Australian Breaking Association in 2020 and 2021 - showcased some of her now-infamous shapes.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Ronson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\"}, {\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999844491853288, \"rank\": 1.3497513094927096e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Captioning the video, Bedggood wrote: \\\"Put it in the Louvre\\\".\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her Olympic performance, Gunn told reporters: \\\"All of my moves are original.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1570, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Creativity is really important to me.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out there, and I show my artistry.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it speaks to the judges, and sometimes it does not.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do my thing, and it represents art.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is what it is about.\\\"\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"University lecturer Gunn was aware that she was no match for her competitors' technical moves, explaining that she instead focused on her \\\"strength\\\" and \\\"creativity\\\".\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You may like to watch    \\\"What I wanted to do was come out here and do something new and different and creative,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best, the dynamic and the power moves, so I wanted to move differently, be artistic and creative because how many chances do you get that in a lifetime to do that on an international stage?\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always the underdog and wanted to make my mark in a different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan's Ami Yuasa took home the gold medal for the B-girls competition in Paris, while Banevi\\u010d earned silver and China's Liu Qingyi took home bronze for their respective performances.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.